00:10:23.890 --> 00:10:25.860
Ethiopia Reads has
been a leader in youth

00:10:25.860 --> 00:10:28.820
and children's literacy
for nearly 20 years.

00:10:28.820 --> 00:10:32.410
Since 1998, Ethiopia Reads has
built more than 70 libraries

00:10:32.410 --> 00:10:34.130
in every region of the country,

00:10:34.130 --> 00:10:36.210
shipped more than a
quarter million books,

00:10:36.210 --> 00:10:39.710
and serves over 130,000
children every year in rural

00:10:39.710 --> 00:10:42.460
and urban communities
throughout Ethiopia.

00:10:42.460 --> 00:10:45.970
We build libraries where there
were none, and often partnering

00:10:45.970 --> 00:10:49.390
with schools to build classroom
libraries for their students.

00:10:49.390 --> 00:10:52.340
And where there were no
schools, we built those two.

00:10:52.340 --> 00:10:55.190
However, after building dozens
of libraries in the schools,

00:10:55.190 --> 00:10:58.470
we still face huge challenges
promoting literacy in Ethiopia.

00:10:58.470 --> 00:11:01.380
After years of working
closely with local communities,

00:11:01.380 --> 00:11:04.620
we've finally understood, instead
of building one new library

00:11:04.620 --> 00:11:07.690
after another, communities simply
wanted to improve the quality

00:11:07.690 --> 00:11:09.860
of reading spaces that
already existed.

00:11:09.860 --> 00:11:12.600
So, over 10 years ago,
Ethiopia reads,

00:11:12.600 --> 00:11:16.740
shifted toward a more
efficient cost-effective program

00:11:16.740 --> 00:11:20.940
by designing projects that were
based on the needs and desires

00:11:20.940 --> 00:11:24.240
of recipients, by listening to
the actual people on the ground.

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:28.960
By avoiding top heavy donor-driven
ideas of development and instead,

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:32.910
by emphasizing the needs and
desires of local stakeholders,

00:11:32.910 --> 00:11:34.380
Ethiopia Reads has been able

00:11:34.380 --> 00:11:37.570
to successfully promote reading
culture throughout Ethiopia,

00:11:37.570 --> 00:11:40.900
not just for the thousands of
young students in the classroom,

00:11:40.900 --> 00:11:43.350
but for their families and
their neighborhoods too.

00:11:43.350 --> 00:11:47.200
Our program, the book-centered
learning program, provides training

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:49.090
and professional development,
so librarians

00:11:49.090 --> 00:11:51.330
and educators can gain
critical skills

00:11:51.330 --> 00:11:54.380 position:56%
and feel supported in the workplace.

00:11:54.380 --> 00:11:58.890
