Program incorporates three elements

00:11:58.890 --> 00:12:00.930
essential to best practices.

00:12:00.930 --> 00:12:03.590
First, professional
training and mentorship,

00:12:03.590 --> 00:12:05.830
on-site with regular follow-up.

00:12:05.830 --> 00:12:07.480
Second, we collect data on site

00:12:07.480 --> 00:12:10.680
which informs the design
of our training program.

00:12:10.680 --> 00:12:13.120
This is an ongoing
collaboration between educators

00:12:13.120 --> 00:12:17.190
and Ethiopia Reads staff members
in Addis, with short feedback loops

00:12:17.190 --> 00:12:20.320
to provide continuous
improvement and innovation.

00:12:20.320 --> 00:12:23.210
Finally, Ethiopia Reads is
an institutional advocate

00:12:23.210 --> 00:12:26.370
for our teachers and librarians,
giving them greater voice

00:12:26.370 --> 00:12:29.780
when working with education
bureaus or government offices

00:12:29.780 --> 00:12:31.980
or local school administrations.

00:12:31.980 --> 00:12:35.220
The Book Centered Learning Program
has been implemented in 22 schools

00:12:35.220 --> 00:12:39.000
across six regions including
Addis Ababa, as well as Southern

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:41.350
and Eastern Ethiopia as well.

00:12:41.350 --> 00:12:44.070
This, I suspect is the main
reason Ethiopia Reads is being

00:12:44.070 --> 00:12:46.000
