beyond the brick and mortar concept

00:12:48.840 --> 00:12:51.260
of development, past
simply building library,

00:12:51.260 --> 00:12:53.770
it's an opening reading
spaces, to embrace the model

00:12:53.770 --> 00:12:55.640
of the delivery services
tailored to the needs

00:12:55.640 --> 00:12:57.840
of the recipients on the ground.

00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:59.310
There are no shortcuts or gimmicks

00:12:59.310 --> 00:13:01.750
to addressing youth and
children's literacy.

00:13:01.750 --> 00:13:04.220
It simply depends on the hard work
being done on the field combined

00:13:04.220 --> 00:13:05.830
with thoughtful planning
that accounts

00:13:05.830 --> 00:13:07.950
for local needs and interest.

00:13:07.950 --> 00:13:09.830
Our experience teaches
the importance

00:13:09.830 --> 00:13:13.630
of a comprehensive literacy model
that addresses issues of access

00:13:13.630 --> 00:13:18.490
and awareness with emphasis
on quality of instruction.

00:13:18.490 --> 00:13:20.130
Ethiopia Reads has impacted

00:13:20.130 --> 00:13:22.590
